Install and make initial setup of
class-validator - Setup middleware on App module level with whitelist of body.
class-transformer - Setup on App module level to transform all body to DTO.
dotenv - Refactor npm script to run project within dotenv.
config - Create configuration file to parse env with default value.
Swagger - Add auto generative OpenApi documentation V1 (path be/doc/v1)
@nestjs/jwt - import with secret from env in AuthService

